    management: "Results guide therapy selection (targeted therapy eligibility), prognosis, and monitoring. HER2 FISH: HER2/CEP17 ratio ≥2.0 = amplified (eligible for trastuzumab). BCR-ABL FISH: monitor CML treatment response. Rapid turnaround: 1-2 days (vs 7-14 days for conventional cytogenetics).",
